# Homepage Premium Redesign — Implementation Plan

## Overview

Redesign all 10 sections of the Bhavyam Properties homepage to achieve a premium, editorial luxury aesthetic. The redesign is guided by the **"Majestic Heritage" design system** generated via Stitch MCP, with the full reference design available locally.

### Generated Design Assets
- **Screenshot:** [homepage-screenshot.png](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/.stitch/designs/homepage-screenshot.png) — full homepage mockup
- **HTML Reference:** [homepage.html](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/.stitch/designs/homepage.html) — open in browser for live preview
- **Design System:** [DESIGN.md](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/.stitch/DESIGN.md) — design tokens reference

> [!TIP]
> Open `.stitch/designs/homepage.html` in your browser right now to see the full generated redesign mockup.

---

## Design System: "Majestic Heritage"

**Stitch Project ID:** `9201326407984821461` | **Screen ID:** `578e514cf45946b6a06ee5c0a46901ae`

| Token | Current | Redesigned |
|---|---|---|
| **Primary Color** | `#00c194` (flat green) | `#112743` Deep Navy + `#006B54` Emerald Heritage |
| **Accent** | `#00b48f` / `#00d09c` (similar greens) | `#00B48F` Emerald Mint + `#00ECBD` / `#38FECE` Electric Mint |
| **Backgrounds** | `#effbf8` / `#f2fcf9` (light green tints) | `#F9FAF8` Warm Ivory + `#F3F4F2` Cloud |
| **Dark Sections** | `#112743` ✅ (keep) | `#001229` → `#112743` gradient |
| **Typography** | Geist (default), inconsistent weights | Inter — Black (900) headlines, Medium (500) body |
| **Border Radius** | Mixed (`rounded-sm` to `rounded-xl`) | Consistent 16–24px rounded, pill-shaped buttons |
| **Shadows** | `shadow-sm` / `shadow-2xl` (harsh) | Ambient shadows (Y:24, Blur:80, 4% opacity) |
| **Borders** | `border-gray-100` solid lines | "No-Line" rule — background shifts only |

