## Proposed Changes — Section by Section

Each section below will be modified in its respective component file. **Only Tailwind classes and markup structure** will change — no logic changes.

---

### 1. Hero Section
#### [MODIFY] [Hero.tsx](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/components/Hero.tsx)

**Current Issues:**
- Emoji icons (🌱🏢🏪💼🏠🗺️) look unprofessional
- Search bar is generic white box
- `rounded-2xl` on mobile, `rounded-full` on desktop — inconsistent

**Redesign:**
- Replace emoji icons with Lucide React icons for property type pills
- Apply glassmorphism to search bar: `bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/30`
- Pill-shaped property type tags with glassmorphism: `bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full border border-white/20`
- Refined gradient overlay: `bg-gradient-to-r from-[#001229]/80 via-[#112743]/50 to-transparent`
- Typography: headline `font-black tracking-[-0.04em]`, tagline `tracking-[0.2em] uppercase`
- Search button: `bg-[#006B54] hover:bg-[#38FECE] hover:text-[#001229] rounded-full`
- Smoother curved SVG divider with ivory (`#F9FAF8`) fill instead of white

---

### 2. Latest Properties Section
#### [MODIFY] [LatestProperties.tsx](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/components/LatestProperties.tsx)

**Current Issues:**
- Cards are `rounded-none` (sharp edges)
- Complex "hanging badge" SVG is visually noisy
- Footer divider line feels heavy

**Redesign:**
- Cards: `rounded-2xl` with ambient shadow
- Remove SVG hanging badge — replace with simple floating pill badge: `rounded-full bg-[#006B54] px-4 py-1`
- Property type badge: `rounded-full` pill style
- Filter tab pills: refined with `bg-[#006B54]` active state, ghost outline for inactive
- Remove bottom divider line — use white background contrast
- "Details" button: `rounded-full` pill shape
- Background: `#F9FAF8` Warm Ivory

---

### 3. About / Why Choose Us Section
#### [MODIFY] [WhyChooseUs.tsx](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/components/WhyChooseUs.tsx)

**Current Issues:**
- Green trapezoid shape looks dated (`clipPath: polygon(...)`)
- "Brush Script MT" cursive watermark looks cheap
- `rounded-sm` button feels sharp

**Redesign:**
- Replace trapezoid with a soft rounded rectangle: `rounded-3xl bg-[#006B54]`
- Remove cursive watermark entirely — replace with subtle `text-[#006B54]/5` large Inter Black text
- Image container: `rounded-2xl overflow-hidden` with ambient shadow
- "Read More" button: `rounded-full bg-[#006B54] text-white hover:bg-[#38FECE] hover:text-[#001229]`
- Dot pattern: keep but reduce opacity further

---

### 4. Services Section
#### [MODIFY] [ServicesSection.tsx](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/components/ServicesSection.tsx)

**Current Issues:**
- Cards have `rounded-lg` and `border-gray-50` (visible border)
- Cursive "Our Service" watermark looks dated
- Background `#effbf8` is a slightly different green tint

**Redesign:**
- Cards: `rounded-2xl` with no border, pure white on `#F3F4F2` background for natural lift
- Remove cursive watermark — replace with subtle Inter label
- Icon containers: `rounded-2xl bg-[#006B54]/10 p-4` soft tinted background
- Hover: `hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_24px_80px_rgba(25,28,27,0.04)]`
- Background: `#F3F4F2` (Cloud)

---

### 5. Expert Solutions Section
#### [MODIFY] [ExpertSolutionsSection.tsx](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/components/ExpertSolutionsSection.tsx)

**Current Issues:**
- Four slightly different green shades are monotonous
- `rounded-lg` cards with basic hover
- Cursive watermark

**Redesign:**
- Gradient progression: `#006B54` → `#00B48F` → `#00ECBD` → `#38FECE` (more dramatic range)
- Cards: `rounded-3xl` with generous padding
- Add glassmorphism overlay on hover: `hover:bg-white/10 hover:backdrop-blur-sm`
- Remove cursive watermark
- Background: `#F9FAF8`

