### 7. Statistics / Counter Section
#### [MODIFY] [CounterSection.tsx](file:///d:/Codes/Panthar/bhavyam-properties/app/web/components/CounterSection.tsx)

**Current Issues:**
- `bg-linear-to-b` (Tailwind v4 syntax may not render in all browsers)
- Cursive "Numbers" watermark
- Counter circles border too subtle

**Redesign:**
- Use gradient: `bg-gradient-to-br from-[#001229] to-[#112743]`
- Remove cursive watermark — replace with Inter
- Counter circles: `border-2 border-white/20 hover:border-[#38FECE]` with glow
- Add shimmer/pulse animation on hover
- City skyline: keep but add subtle opacity gradient

