## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Placeholder images**: The Blog and Testimonials sections currently use `placehold.co` images. Should I generate real placeholder images using the image generation tool, or keep them as-is?
> 2. **Cursive watermarks**: The current design uses "Brush Script MT" cursive watermarks behind each section heading. The redesign removes them. Are you OK with this, or do you want an alternative decorative element?
> 3. **Emoji icons in Hero**: I plan to replace emojis (🌱🏢🏪) with Lucide React SVG icons. `lucide-react` is already a dependency. Confirmed OK?

